Spread each of 6 crackers with 1 teaspoon. of the peanut butter; cover with second cracker to form 'spiders body.' Insert 8 pretzel sticks into the peanut butter layer of each spider for the 'legs.' Spread 1 teaspoon of the remaining peanut butter onto top of each spider. Decorate with sprinkles, then add 2 currants to each for the 'eyes.'